        <description>&lt;p&gt;     We are HG021B group, column Shanghai Xuhui, the logo is a purple rabbit exploring from a gentleman&amp;rsquo;s hat. The combination of the gentleman&amp;rsquo;s hat and the exploration rabbit is like a &amp;ldquo;rabbit hole&amp;rdquo;, which is a symbol of our exploration in the unknown offensive and defensive world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Core goal: to promote the development of network security, adhering to the spirit of the hacker club to share technology with the public and make common progress.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Research direction: vulnerability analysis, shooting range, AWD, CTF&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
